<p>Sci-fi panel. Made according to references from the Internet.</p>

<p>The challenge is aimed at studying:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Program interface</li>
  <li>Functionality</li>
  <li>The main workflow</li>
  <li>Further application of materials in other programs</li>
</ul>

<p>Used programs:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Substance Designer</li>
  <li>Marmoset Toolbag 4</li>
  <li>Illustrator</li>
</ul>

